theorem Topology.closure_diff_boundary_eq_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    closure A \ (closure A \ interior A) = interior A := by
  classical
  have h_compl :
      (closure A \ interior A)ᶜ =
        interior A ∪ (closure A)ᶜ := by
    simpa using
      Topology.compl_boundary_eq_union_interior_compl_closure
        (X := X) (A := A)
  calc
    closure A \ (closure A \ interior A)
        = closure A ∩ ((closure A \ interior A)ᶜ) := by
          simp [Set.diff_eq]
    _ = closure A ∩ (interior A ∪ (closure A)ᶜ) := by
          simp [h_compl]
    _ = (closure A ∩ interior A) ∪ (closure A ∩ (closure A)ᶜ) := by
          simp [Set.inter_distrib_left]
    _ = interior A ∪ (closure A ∩ (closure A)ᶜ) := by
          simp [Set.inter_comm]
    _ = interior A ∪ (∅ : Set X) := by
          simp [Set.inter_compl_self]
    _ = interior A := by
          simp

theorem Set.inter_distrib_left {α : Type*} {s t u : Set α} :
    s ∩ (t ∪ u) = (s ∩ t) ∪ (s ∩ u) := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hx
    rcases hx with ⟨hx_s, hxtu⟩
    cases hxtu with
    | inl hx_t => exact Or.inl ⟨hx_s, hx_t⟩
    | inr hx_u => exact Or.inr ⟨hx_s, hx_u⟩
  · intro hx
    cases hx with
    | inl hst => exact ⟨hst.1, Or.inl hst.2⟩
    | inr hsu => exact ⟨hsu.1, Or.inr hsu.2⟩
